This paper deals with formalizing and reasoning about the quality of software and hardware systems, which falls under the domain of formal methods and software engineering. The paper introduces an augmentation by discounting of Linear Temporal Logic (LTL) and studies its combination with propositional quality operators, which suggests that the paper could be categorized under logic (cs.LO), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), software engineering (cs.SE), programming languages (cs.PL), and machine learning (cs.LG).
